<h2 class="n">Portland Christian Center Choir</h2>
<p class="highlight">The Portland Christian Center Choir has the privilege of leading the church in worship each week.</p>
<p>Our calling as worship leaders is to lift up Jesus Christ, to extol Him with music and song, and to praise Him with all of our heart mind and strength.</p>
<p>Being a part of the Portland Christian Center Choir will not only change your life, but will directly impact hundreds of lives for the glory of God. From Sunday services to special concerts, recording projects and choir tours, the PCC Choir is a high impact ministry.</p>
<h3>Want to Join The Portland Christian Center Choir?</h3>
